# Pipeline Config

## Stages

| Stage | Description | Exit criteria |
|-------|-------------|---------------|
| Seed | Identified — no meaningful contact yet | First response or meeting booked |
| Nurture | Engaged — active conversation or drip in progress | Qualified interest confirmed |
| Active | Qualified — evaluating or in proposal stage | Decision reached |
| Won | Closed successfully | — |
| Dropped | Disqualified or abandoned | — |

## Stale Threshold

> A prospect is flagged as stale when their last interaction is older than this many days.
> The pipeline overview card uses this value to surface who needs attention.

14

